\p
\v 1 Ngasengibona ingilosi isehla ivela ezulwini, ilesihluthulelo\x + 9.1. 1.18.\x* somgodi ongelamkhawulo\x + 20.3. 9.1. 20.10.\x*, leketane elikhulu esandleni sayo.
\v 2 Yasiwubamba umgobho\x + 12.3.\x*, inyoka endala\x + 12.9.\x*, enguDiyabhola\x + 20.10.\x* loSathane\x + 20.7. 2.9.\x*, yasiwubopha okweminyaka eyinkulungwane\x + 2 Pet. 2.4. Juda 1.6.\x*,
\v 3 yasiwuphosela emgodini ongelamkhawulo\x + 20.3. 9.1. 20.10.\x*, yawuvalela, yasibeka uphawu phezu kwawo\x + Dan. 6.17.\x*, ukuze ungabe usaduhisa izizwe, ize iphele iminyaka eyinkulungwane\x + 12.9.\x*\x + 20.8,10.\x*; lemva kwalokhu kumele ukuthi ukhululwe okwesikhatshana.
\s Ukuvuka kokuqala
\p
\v 4 Ngasengibona izihlalo zobukhosi\x + Dan. 7.9. Mat. 19.28. Isam. 2.26; 3.21.\x*, basebehlala kuzo\x + Luka 12.20. 1 Kho. 22.19.\x*, lokwahlulela kwanikelwa kubo\x + Dan. 7.22,27. 1 Kor. 6.2.\x*; \add ngabona\add* lemiphefumulo\x + 6.9.\x* yalabo ababequnywe amakhanda\x + 11.8.\x* ngenxa yobufakazi bukaJesu\x + 1.2.\x* langenxa yelizwi likaNkulunkulu\x + 1.2.\x*, lababengakhonzanga isilo\x + 13.12.\x*, loba umfanekiso waso\x + 13.15.\x*, njalo bengemukelanga uphawu lwaso ebunzini labo, lesandleni sabo\x + 13.16.\x*; basebephila babusa kanye loKristu\x + Dan. 7.18. 2 Tim. 2.12. Isam. 5.10. 20.6. Hlab. 45.16.\x* iminyaka eyinkulungwane\x + 20.2,3,5,6,7.\x*.
\v 5 Kodwa abaseleyo kwabafileyo kabaphindanga baphila\x + Roma 7.9.\x* ize iphele iminyaka eyinkulungwane\x + 20.2,3,5,6,7.\x*. Lokhu kuyikuvuka kokuqala\x + 1 Thes. 4.16. Luka 14.14.\x*.
\v 6 Ubusisiwe njalo ungcwele olesabelo ekuvukeni kokuqala\x + 14.13.\x*; phezu kwalaba ukufa kwesibili kakulamandla\x + 2.11. 20.14. 21.8.\x*, kodwa bazakuba ngabapristi bakaNkulunkulu, labakaKristu\x + 1.6.\x*, njalo bazabusa kanye laye\x + Dan. 7.18. 2 Tim. 2.12. Isam. 5.10. 20.6. Hlab. 45.16.\x* iminyaka eyinkulungwane\x + 20.2,3,5,6,7.\x*.
