\v 7 Lalapho isiphelile iminyaka eyinkulungwane\x + 20.2,3,5,6,7.\x*, uSathane uzakhululwa\x + 20.7. 2.9.\x* entolongweni yakhe\x + 20.2. 1 Pet. 3.19.\x*,
\v 8 njalo uzaphumela ukuduhisa izizwe\x + 20.3,10. 12.9.\x* ezisemagumbini amane omhlaba\x + 7.1.\x*, uGogi loMagogi\x + Hez. 38.2; 39.1. Gen. 10.2.\x*, ukubabuthela\x + 16.14.\x* empini\x + 1 Kor. 14.8.\x*; onani labo lingangetshebetshebe lolwandle\x + Roma 9.27. Heb. 11.12. Gen. 22.17.\x*.
