\s Ukwahlulela kokucina
\p
\v 11 Ngasengibona isihlalo sobukhosi esikhulu lesimhlophe lohlezi kuso, omhlaba lezulu kwabalekela ubuso bakhe\x + 21.1. Hlab. 102.26.\x*, njalo kakutholelwanga ndawo\x + Dan. 2.35.\x*.
\v 12 Ngasengibona abafileyo abancinyane labakhulu\x + Seb. 26.22.\x*, bemi phambi kukaNkulunkulu, lengwalo zavulwa\x + Dan. 7.10.\x*; njalo olunye ugwalo lwavulwa, olungolwempilo\x + 20.15. Dan. 12.1. Isam. 3.5.\x*; abafileyo basebesahlulelwa ngezinto ezibhalwe ezingwalweni\x + 11.18.\x*, ngokwemisebenzi yabo\x + 20.13. 2.23.\x*.
\v 13 Lolwandle lwabakhupha abafileyo ababekilo, njalo ukufa\x + 6.8.\x* lesihogo\f + \fk isihogo: \fl kumbe, \fq ingcwaba.\f* kwakhupha abafileyo ababekikho\x + Fil. 2.10.\x*; basebesahlulelwa, ngulowo lalowo, ngokwemisebenzi yabo\x + 20.13. 2.23.\x*.
\v 14 Ukufa lesihogo\x + 1 Kor. 15.26,54. Isam. 21.4.\x* kwasekuphoselwa echibini lomlilo\x + 20.14,15. 19.20.\x*; lokhu kuyikufa kwesibili\x + 20.6.\x*.
\v 15 Uba-ke ekhona ongatholwanga elotshiwe egwalweni lwempilo\x + 20.15. Dan. 12.1. Isam. 3.5.\x*, waphoselwa echibini lomlilo\x + 20.14,15. 19.20.\x*.